  <title>Gear Module</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Gear<keyword>Circular Pitch</keyword><keyword>Module</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Circular Pitch</text><text styleclass="Popup Box"> is the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">circumference of gear / number of teeth</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2" style="margin-left:15px;"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Circular Pitch: </text><equation styleclass="VariableName-small;vertical-align:text-bottom" font-size="22" color="#000000"><![CDATA[P=\lfrac{\pi.d}{N}]]></equation></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2"></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Gear Module</text> is the metric size of the gear tooth<text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">To get <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Module</text>, we drop the irrational number,<text styleclass="VariableName-small"> &#160;</text><equation styleclass="VariableName-small"><![CDATA[\pi]]></equation><text styleclass="Body Text"> ,</text> from <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Circular Pitch</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="margin-left:15px;"><equation styleclass="VariableName-small"><![CDATA[\therefore]]></equation><text styleclass="VariableName-small"> Gear Module:</text>&#32;<equation style="vertical-align:text-bottom"><![CDATA[m=\lfrac{P}{\pi}\ \ = \ \ \lfrac{d}{N}]]></equation></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="margin-left:15px;"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Gear Module (m) = P.C.D. (mm) &#160;∕ &#160;number-of-teeth</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="margin-left:15px;">Units are <text styleclass="VariableName-small">mm</text>, but they are usually omitted<text styleclass="VariableName-small">&#32;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Gear-Module-Standard">Industry Standard Modules</link></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Gear-PCD">PCD - definition</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
